{"tid":1724214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞重溫] 鉛水拉勻一生論","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:59:33.000Z","uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"56cff7ff82b43c5d22c9ca7aad2b64fcba5f1fd4","tid":1724214,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"2015年7月14日，衛生防護中心監測及流行病學處主任程卓端指出，若「一生拉勻」計，飲用水的含鉛量平均低於世衛標準，亦即每公升不多於10微克鉛的話，不會明顯威脅健康。翌日她否認自己涼薄，只表示其言論概念「比較難明白」，但啟晴邨及葵聯邨食水含鉛量只屬輕微超標，只要不是長時期飲用，就不用太擔心。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UsEO7Y5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUsEO7Y5.jpg&h=85ab1fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死mon post 曱甴唔洗怕二噁英喎，拉勻一世都係好少咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ec46c744e6d2beea14cd834b5ea6f5a9080dde66","tid":1724214,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"拉勻一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d663691aa9ae035c091d70cc4d8c36676bc13c8b","tid":1724214,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"f5d1b038a54e05e5e994879c5f55e18c34e74ea1","tid":1724214,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"}]}